hadiths[40]{hadithnumber,text}:
294,"ham Haj ke irade se nikley. jab ham maqam sarf mein pahunchey to main haaiza ho gaee aur us ranj mein rone lagi ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laaey, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha tumhen kya ho gaya. kya haaiza ho gaee ho. maine kaha, haan ! Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye aik aisi cheez hai jis ko Allah Taala ne Adam ki betiyon ke liye likh diya hai. isliye tum bhi Haj ke arkaan poorey kar lo. albatta Baitullah ka tawaaf na karna. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni beeviyon ki taraf se gaaey ki qurbani ki. (sarf aik maqam Makka se 6-7 meel ke faasle par hai)."
295,main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sar Mubarak ko haaiza honey ki haalat mein bhi kangha kya karti thi.
296,"unse sawal kya gaya, kya haaiza biwi meri khidmat kar sakti hai, ya napaki ki haalat mein aurat mujh se nazdeek ho sakti hai? Urwa ne farmaya mere nazdeek to usmein koi harj nahi hai. is tarah ki auratein meri bhi khidmat karti hain aur is mein kisi ke liye bhi koi harj nahi. isliye ke mujhey Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne khabar di ke wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko haaiza honey ki haalat mein kangha kya karti thin aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us waqt masjid mein motakif hotey . aap apna sar Mubarak qareeb kar detey aur Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) apne hujre hi se kangha kar diya kartii thin, halanke wo haaiza hotiin."
297,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) meri god mein sar rakh kar Quran Majeed padhtey , halanke main us waqt haiz wali hoti thi."
298,"main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aik chadar mein leti hui thi, itney mein mujhey haiz aa gaya. isliye main aahista se bahar nikal aai aur apne haiz ke kapdey pahan liye. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha kya tumhen nifaas aa gaya hai? maine arz kya haan. phir mujhey Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bula liya, aur main chadar mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath let gaee."
299,"unhon-ne farmaya main aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik hi bartan mein ghusl kartey they, halanke donon junbi (hambistari k baad ki napaki ki haalat me) hotey ."
300,"aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mujhey hukm farmatey, isliye main izaar baandh leti , phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mere sath hambistari kartey, us waqt main haaiza hoti."
301,aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apna sar Mubarak meri taraf kar detey. us waqt Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aetikaf mein baithey huey hotey aur main haiz ki haalat mein honey ke bawajud Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka sar Mubarak dho deti.
302,"aap ne farmaya ham beeviyon mein se koi jab haaiza hoti, us haalat main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) agar mubashrat ka irada kartey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) izaar baandhney ka hukm de detey bawajud haiz ki zyadti ke. phir badan se badan milaate , aap ne kaha tum mein aisa kon hai jo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki tarah apni shahwat par qaabu rakhta ho. is hadis ki mutabiat (pairavi) Khalid aur Jarir ne Shebani ki riwayat se ki hai. ( yahan bhi mubashrat se sath letnaa baithna murad hai)."
303,"jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni beeviyon mein se kisi se mubashrat karna chahtey aur wo haaiza hoti, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hukm se, wo pahley izaar baandh letin aur Sufiyan ne Shebani se usko riwayat kya hai."
304,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) eidul-Azha ya eidul-fitr mein eidgaah tashrif ley gaey. wahan Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aurton ke paas se guzrey aur farmaya aey aurton ki jamat ! sadqa karo, kyonke maine jahannam mein zyada tum hi ko dekha hai. unhon-ne kaha ya Rasulullah ! aisa kyon ? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum la'an- ta'an bahut karti ho aur shauhar ki na-shukri karti ho, bawajud aql aur Deen mein naaqis honey ke maine tum se zyada kisi ko bhi aik aqlmand aur tajriba kaar aadmi ko deewaanaa bana dene wala nahi dekha. aurton ne kaha ke hamarey Deen aur hamari aql mein nuqsan kya hai ya Rasulullah ? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya kya aurat ki gawahi mard ki gawahi se aadhi nahi hai? unhon-ne kaha, ji hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya bas yahi uski aql ka nuqsan hai. phir aap ne puchha kya aisa nahi hai ke jab aurat haaiza ho to na Namaz padh sakti hai na roza rakh sakti hai, aurton ne kaha aisa hi hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke yahi iske Deen ka nuqsan hai."
305,"ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Haj ke liye is tarah nikley ke hamari zabanon par Haj ke ilawa aur koi zikr hi na tha. jab ham maqam sarf pahunchey to mujhey haiz aa gaya. (is gham se) mein ro rahi thi ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laaey, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha ke kyon ro rahi ho? maine kaha kash! ! main us saal Haj ka irada hi na karti . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya shayad tumhen haiz aa gaya hai. maine kaha ji haan. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ye cheez to Allah Taala ne Adam ki betiyon ke liye muqarrar kar di hai. isliye tum jab tak paak na ho jao tawaaf Baitullah ke ilawa haajiyon ki tarah tamam kaam anjam do."
306,"Fatima abi Habish ki beti ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha ke ya Rasulullah ! main to paak hi nahi hoti, to kya main Namaz bilkul chhod dun. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye rag ka khoon hai haiz nahi isliye jab haiz ke din (jin mein kabhi pahley tumhein aadatan aayaa karta tha) aaein to Namaz chhod de aur jab andaza ke mutabiq wo din guzar jayen, to khoon dho daal aur Namaz padh."
307,"aik aurat ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se sawal kya. us ne puchha ke ya Rasulullah ! aap aik aisi aurat ke mutaalliq kya farmatey hain jiske kapdey par haiz ka khoon lag gaya ho. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar kisi aurat ke kapdey par haiz ka khoon lag jaey to chahiye ke usey ragad daaley, iske baad usey pani se dhoey , phir us kapdey mein Namaz padh ley."
308,"aap ne farmaya ke hamein haiz aata to kapdey ko paak kartey waqt ham khoon ko mil detey, phir us jagah ko dho letey aur tamam kapdey par pani baha detey aur usey pahan kar Namaz padhtey ."
309,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki kuchh beeviyon ne aetikaf kya, halanke wo haiz ki haalat mein thin aur unhein khoon aata tha. isliye khoon ki wjah se tasht aksar apne nichey rakh letin aur Ikrima ne kaha ke Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kusum ka pani dekha to farmaya ye to aisa hi malum hota hai jaisey falan saahiba ko istihaza ka khoon aata tha."
310,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki beeviyon mein se aik ne aetikaf kya. wo khoon aur zardi ( nikaltey ( dekhteen , tasht unke nichey hota aur Namaz ada karti thin."
311,kuchh ummahaatul momeneen (nabi ki beeviyon) ne aetikaf kya halanke wo haiz ki haalat me hoti thin. (oopar wali riwayat mein un hi ka zikr hai).
312,"hamarey paas sirf aik kapda hota tha, jisey ham haiz ke waqt pahnte they. jab usmein khoon lag jata to is par thook daal letey aur phir usey nakhunon se masal detey."
313,"hamein kisi maiyat par teen din se zyada sog karne se mana kya jata tha. lekin shauhar ki maut par char mahiney das din ke sog ka hukm tha. un dinon mein ham na surma lagaateen na khushbu aur asab ( Yaman ki bani hui aik chadar jo rangeen bhi hoti thi) ke ilawa koi rangeen kapda ham istemal nahi karti thin aur hamein ( iddat ke dinon mein) haiz ke ghusl ke baad kuste-azfaar istemal karne ki ijazat thi aur hamein janaaze ke peechhey chalney se mana kya jata tha. us hadis ko Hisham bin Hassan ne Hafsa se, unhon-ne umme-Atiiyaa se, unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat kya hai."
314,"aik ansariya aurat ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha ke main haiz ka ghusl kaisey karun. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke mashk mein basaa hua kapda lekar us se paakii hasil kar. usne poochha. isse kis tarah paakii hasil karun Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, us se paakii hasil kar. usne dobara puchha ke kis tarah? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya Subhan-Allah ! paakii hasil kar. phir maine usey apni taraf kheench liya aur kaha ke usey khoon lagi hui jaghon par pher liya kar."
315,"ansariya aurat ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha ke main haiz ka ghusl kaisey karun. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aik mashk mein basaa hua kapda ley aur paakii hasil kar, ye Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne teen baar farmaya, phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sharmaaey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apna chehra Mubarak pher liya, ya farmaya ke us se paakii hasil kar. phir maine unhein pakad kar kheench liya aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jo baat kahnii chahtey they wo maine usey samjhaaii ."
316,"maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Hijjatul-wada kya, main tamatto karne walon mein thi aur qurbani ka janwar (yani qurbani ka janwar ( apne sath nahi ley gaee thi. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne apne mutaalliq bataya ke phir wo haaiza ho gain aur Arfa ki raat aa gaee aur abhi tak wo paak nahi hui thin. isliye unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha ke ya Rasulullah ! aaj Arfa ki raat hai aur main Umra ki niyat kar chuki thi, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke apne sar ko khol daal aur kangha kar aur Umra ko chhod de. maine aisa hi kya. phir maine Haj pura kya aur lailatul-hasbaa mein Abdur-Rehman bin Abu-Bakar ko Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hukm diya. wo mujhey us Umra ke badla mein jiski niyat maine ki thi taneem se ( doosra ( Umra kara laey."
317,ham Zil-Hijja ka chaand dekhtey hi nikley. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jiska dil chahey to usey Umre ka ehram baandh lena chahiye kyonke agar main qurbani ka janwar sath na laataa to main bhi Umre ka ehram baandhtaa . is par kuchh sahaba ne Umre ka ehram baandha aur kuchh ne Haj kaa. main bhi un logon mein se thi jinhoney Umre ka ehram baandha tha. magar Arfa ka din aa gaya aur main haiz ki haalat mein thi. maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se iske mutaalliq shikayat ki to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Umra chhod aur apna sar khol aur kangha kar aur Haj ka ehram baandh ley. maine aisa hi kya. yahan tak ke jab hasba ki raat aai to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mere sath mere bhai Abdur-Rehman -bin-abi-Bakr ko bhejaa. mein taneem mein gaee aur wahan se apne Umra ke badley doosrey Umre ka ehram baandhaa. Hisham ne kaha ke unmein se kisi baat ki wjah se bhi na qurbani ka janwar wajib hui aur na roza aur na sadqa .) taneem had haram se qareeb teen mail door aik maqam ka naam hai).
318,"Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke maa k pet mein Allah Taala ne aik farishta muqarrar kya hai. wo kehta hai ke aey rab! ab ye ( نطفة ( hai, aey rab! ab ye ( علقة (ho gaya hai, aey rab! ab ye ( مضغة‏ (ho gaya hai. phir jab Allah chahta hai ke uski khilqat poori karey to kehta hai ke muzakkar ya muannas, bad-bakht hai ya nek bakht, rozii kitni muqaddar hai aur umr kitnii. to maa ke pet hi mein ye tamam baatein farishta likh deta hai."
319,"ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Hijjatul-wada ke safar mein nikley, ham mein se kuchh ne Umre ka ehram baandha aur kuchh ne Haj ka, phir ham Makka aaey aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jisne Umre ka ehram baandha ho aur qurbani ka janwar sath na laya ho to wo halal ho jaey aur jisne Umre ka ehram baandha ho aur wo qurbani ka janwar bhi sath laya ho to wo qurbani ke janwar ki qurbani se pahley halal na hoga aur jisne Haj ka ehram baandha ho to usey Haj pura karna chahiye Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ke main haaiza ho gaee aur Arfa ka din aa gaya. maine sirf Umre ka ehram baandha tha mujhey Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hukm diya ke main apna sar khol loon, kangha kar loon aur Haj ka ehram baandh loon aur Umra chhod dun, maine aisa hi kya aur apna Haj pura kar liya. phir mere sath Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Abdur-Rehman -bin-abi-Bakr ko bheja aur mujh se farmaya ke main apne chhotey huey Umra ke iwaz taneem se doosra Umra karun."
320,Fatima binte- abii-Habeesh ko istihaza ka khoon aaya karta tha. to unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se iske mutaalliq poochha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye rag ka khoon hai aur haiz nahi hai. isliye jab haiz ke din aaein to Namaz chhod diya kar aur jab haiz ke din guzar jayen to ghusl karke Namaz padh liya kar.
321,jis zamane mein ham paak rahtey hain. ( haiz se) kya hamarey liye usi zamana ki Namaz kafi hai. is par Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya ke kya tum harooriya ho? ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamane main haaiza hoti thin aur aap hamein Namaz ka hukm nahi detey they. ya Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne ye farmaya ke ham Namaz nahi padhti thin.
322,"main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath chadar mein leti hui thi ke mujhey haiz aa gaya, isliye main chupkey se nikal aai aur apne haiz ke kapdey pahan liye. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, kya tumhen haiz aa gaya hai? maine kaha ji haan. phir mujhey aap ne bula liya aur apne sath chadar mein dakhil kar liya. Zenab ne kaha ke mujh se Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) rozey se hotey aur usi haalat mein unka bosa letey aur maine aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik hi bartan mein janabat ka ghusl kya."
323,"main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aik chadar mein leti hui thi ke mujhey haiz aa gaya, mein chupkey se chali gaee aur haiz ke kapdey badal liye, aap ne puchha kya tujh ko haiz aa gaya hai. maine kaha, ji haan ! phir mujhey aap ne bula liya aur main aap ke sath chadar mein let gaee."
324,"ham apni kunwaarii jawan bachchiyon ko eidgaah janey se rokti thin, phir aik aurat aai aur bani Khalaf ke mahal mein utriin aur unhon-ne apni behan (umme-Atiya (ke hawale se bayan kya, jinke shauhar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath 12 ladaaiyon mein Sharik huey they aur khud unki apni behan apne shauhar ke sath 6 jangon mein gaee thin. unhon-ne bayan kya ke ham zakhmiyon ki marham patti kya karti thin aur mareezon ki khabargeerii bhi karti thin. meri behan ne aik martaba Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha ke agar ham mein se kisi ke paas chadar na ho to kya uske liye usmein koi harj hai ke wo (namaaze-eid ke liye) bahar na nikley. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya uski sathi aurat ko chahiye ke apni chadar ka kuchh hissey usey bhi udha de, phir wo khair ke mauqon par aur musalmanon ki duaon mein Sharik hon, (yani eidgaah jaaein) phir jab umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anhu) aaein to maine unse bhi yahi sawal kya. unhon-ne farmaya, mera bap aap par fidaa ho, haan Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye farmaya tha aur umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anhu) jab bhi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka zikr kartin to ye zaroor farmaatiin ke mera bap Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par fidaa ho. (unhon-ne kaha) maine aapko ye kehtey huey suna tha ke jawan ladkiyaan, parde waaliyaan aur haaiza auratein bhi bahar niklin aur khair main aur musalmanon ki duaon mein Sharik hon aur haaiza aurat jaae-namaaz se door rahe. Hafsa kehti hain, maine puchha kya haaiza bhi ? to unhon-ne farmaya ke wo Arafaat main aur falan-falan jagah nahi jati. yani jab wo un jumla muqaddas maqamat mein jati hain to phir eidgaah kyon na jaaein."
325,"Fatima binte-abi-Hubaish (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha ke mujhey istihaza ka khoon aata hai aur main paak nahi ho paatii , to kya main Namaz chhod diya karun? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya nahi. ye to aik rag ka khoon hai, haan itney dinon mein Namaz zaroor chhod diya kar jin mein us bimari se pahley tumhen haiz aaya karta tha. phir ghusl karke Namaz padha karo."
326,ham zard aur matyaley rang ko koi ahmiyat nahi deti thin.
327,(jo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki biwi hain) ke Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anhu) saat (7) saal tak haiz ki haalat mein rahen. unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se iske barey mein puchha to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein ghusl karne ka hukm diya aur farmaya ke ye rag (ki wjah se bimari ( hai. to Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anhu) har Namaz ke liye ghusl karti thin.
328,"unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha ke ya Rasulullah! Safiya binte- huyii (Raziallahu anhu) ko (haj mein) haiz aa gaya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, shayad ke wo hamein rokengi. kya unhon-ne tumharey sath tawaaf ( ziyaarat ( nahi kya. aurton ne jawab diya ke kar liya hai. aap ne is par farmaya ke phir niklo."
329,haaiza ke liye (jab ke usne tawaaf ifaaza kar liya ho) rukhsat hai ke wo ghar jaey (aur tawaaf wadaa' ke liye na ruki rahe).
330,usey (baghair tawaafe-wadaa' ke) jana nahi chahiye phir maine unhein kehtey huey suna ke chali jaey kyonke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unko uski rukhsat di hai.
331,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jab haiz ka zamana aaey to Namaz chhod de aur jab ye zamana guzar jaey to khoon ko dho aur Namaz padh .
332,"aik aurat ( umme-Kab ( zachgi mein mar gaee, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unki namaze-janaza padhi, us waqt Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unke ( jism ke) beech mein khadey ho gaey."
333,maine apni khala Memuna (Raziallahu anha) se jo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki paak bevi thin suna ke main haaiza hoti to Namaz nahi padhti thi aur ye ke aap Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke) ghar mein) Namaz padhney ki jagah ke qareeb leti hoti thi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Namaz apni chatai par padhtey . jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sajda kartey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke kapdey ka koi hissey mujh se lag jata tha.
